Geography==
* Region - [[Zona da Mata (coastal)|Zona da mata Pernambucana]] * Boundaries - [[Tracunhaém]] ('''N'''), [[São Lourenço da Mata]], [[Chã de Alegria]], [[Camaragibe]] and [[Glória do Goitá]] ('''S'''), [[Carpina]] and [[Lagoa do Itaenga]] ('''W'''), [[Paulista]] and [[Abreu e Lima]] ('''E''') * Hydrography - [[Capibaribe River|Capibaribe]] and [[Goiana River|Goiana]] rivers * Vegetation - [[Subcaducifólia]] forest * Climate - Hot tropical and humid * Annual average temperature - {{convert|25.2|C|F}} * Distance to [[Recife]] - {{convert|42|km|mi}}
==Economy==
The main economic activities in '''Paudalho''' are based in extrativism{{Clarify|reason=|date=January 2018|post-text=(Misspelled? Poor translation from Portuguese?)}} industry, commerce and primary sector especially [[sugarcane]] and [[cattle]].
